Package net.delugan.teachly.user

Class User

java.lang.Object
net.delugan.teachly.utils.DateTracked
net.delugan.teachly.user.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class User extends DateTracked implements Serializable
Entity class representing a user in the system. Stores user profile information and authentication details.
